OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLGBT veteran in 'last      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbattle' for army ban       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcompensation               
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A veteran who was sacked from the Navy 
OL,6, for his sexuality says he fears he will
OL,7, die before he gets compensation from   
OL,8, the UK government.                     
OL,10,FJoe Ousalice was one of thousands who  
OL,11,Fwere affected by a ban on LGBT people  
OL,12,Fserving in the British military.       
OL,14,FLast year the prime minister said the  
OL,15,Fban, which lasted until 2000, was an   
OL,16,F"appalling failure", and those affected
OL,17,Fhave been promised compensation.       
OL,19,FMr Ousalice, 73, says he now has cancer
OL,20,Fand is yet to receive any money.       
